9.4 DUIM-Frames Module

menu-item-name

Generic function

Summary

Returns the name of the specified menu item.

Signature

menu-item-name menu-item => name

Arguments

menu-item
An instance of type <command-table-menu-item>.

Values

name
An instance of type <string>.

Library

duim-frames

Module

duim-frames

Description

Returns the name of menu-item.

See also

menu-item-options, page 833

menu-item-type, page 834

menu-item-value, page 834
